Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: ltest
Version: 2.0.0
Summary: A package for lazy people who test things
Home-page: https://github.com/wmak/ltest
Author: William Mak
Author-email: william@wmak.io
License: UNKNOWN
Description: # To run 
        ```bash
        ltest -d <file to monitor> -c <command to run>
        ```
        
        ## Example
        This will run `make html` whenever ltest notices a change in the current folder
        ```bash
        ltest -d ./ -c make html
        ```
        
